1934;;The Lady is Willing;;British;;Gilbert Miller;;Leslie Howard, Cedric Hardwicke;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Lady_Is_Willing_(1934_film);;Set in France, private detective Albert Latour is employed by three men who aim to take revenge on the man responsible for a failed investment. Realising that the man's wife is wealthy, Latour kidnaps her in order to hold a ransom. The matter gets complicated when he finds himself falling in love with her.[1]